  "description": "<p>As for the “Races/Homeworlds/Territory” table, that simply acts as a three-in-one table. Need a quick canon-specific <em>Star Wars</em> race? Roll on the table, and automatically know its homeworld and where it is located. Or, need a random planet for your character(s) to go do a mission on? Roll on this same table. (<em>Example: If you roll up Bothan / Bothawui / Mid Rim, this could serve as either you’ve encountered a Bothan, been assigned a mission to Bothawui, or met someone from the Mid Rim.</em>)</p>",
